Dinho (Gremio) missed, Kluivert (Ajax) missed, Arce (Gremio) missed, Ronald de
Boer (Ajax) scored, Magno (Gremio) scored, Frank de Boer (Ajax) scored, Gelson
(Gremio) scored, George (Ajax) scored, Adilson (Gremio) scored, Blind (Ajax)
scored.
