(Germany), A Lacy (USA), M Arruti (Spain), R Bates (USA), M Burstrom (Sweden).
76 - K Ross, R Comstock (USA), C Peek (USA), L Irvine, E Rundle, E
Britchford-Steel, W Fryer.
BILL JOHNSON
