<RECORDNO>975143040</RECORDNO>
<TEXT>
A NEW show flat at College Lands, in Glasgow's Merchant City, has been opened
by Miller Homes to mark the release of a new phase of one- and two-bed flats.
The interior has been designed by Brian Swinton, who says it has a strong
